{"tid":1472040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解老共唔夠膽搞機場? 係因為機場有外國人!","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:09:06.000Z","uid":267711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f043e28cc280e35b6c2a2951734e48369b7bcba","tid":1472040,"uid":267711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:29:24.000Z","msg":"忽發奇想, 如果每次遊行中間都有外國人(最好係美國人), 老共敢唔敢用武力鎮壓?<br />\n對於老共黎講,一個美國公民條命緊要過十萬個香港人<br />\n我建議將遊行變成香港特色活動, 每月一次 (每次十萬香港人就夠), 最緊要鼓勵外國人參與 (可以向佢地提供經濟Support, 住宿等等), 相信好多Backpacker會樂意參與<br />\n<br />\n只要香港持續有民主抗爭活動, 一定可以對內輸出革命, <br />\n<br />\n我地要贏, 一定要connect全世界, 要救香港, 未必一定要攬炒,反而要將國際城市嘅優點發輝到極致 (即係使其他國家成為香港嘅Stakeholder), 實行搞個聯合國遊行, 將香港變成逆權之都"},{"pid":"ea1cf1fbcebf791cdac51770e27beb501e229aee","tid":1472040,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4kdK7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4kdK7K.jpg&h=8672802c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv9iuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv9iuk.jpg&h=da06f494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警護送荃灣黑夜斬人兇手離開機場</span></span>"},{"pid":"243126dbf11ca8dfdadc2f3c9fd377a586156e5e","tid":1472040,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:09:06.000Z","msg":"不如LIHKG 以後只可以開一個集中討論PO 做反思, 檢討<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472214</a>"}]}